Description: An efficient R wrapper for the CISNET Smoking History Generator.
    The version number follows the scheme <engine>-<wrapper> (e.g. 6.5.3-1.0.0),
    where the first part tracks the bundled C++ engine (SHGMostRecentTag) and the
    second part is the independent R wrapper release (RWrapperVersion).
